PyxisMap was developed by HudsonAlpha Institute for Biotechnology to simplify and improve the accuracy of ranking genes from phenotypic information. This License and Terms of Use outlines the terms and conditions under which User may use PyxisMap. By using PyxisMap, User acknowledges and agrees to be bound by This License and Terms of Use. PyxisMap may be used for non-commercial, research purposes only.

