“HudsonAlpha” means HudsonAlpha Institute for Biotechnology, an Alabama nonprofit corporation located at 601 Genome Way, Huntsville, Alabama.

“PyxisMap” means the web-based tool available for research use only on the HudsonAlpha website at pyxis.hudsonalpha.org.

“User” means any person or entity that accesses the HudsonAlpha website and uses PyxisMap.

